
Multiple Vendors for a particular service: V1, V2, V3
Cost of each vendor: C1, C2, C3

Example: SMS Gateway, or internal SMS Delivery Service
Goal: To always send the SMS on the request by any downstream service


Flow after the SMS Service receives a SEND SMS request:
1. Payload validation
2. Choose Best Vendor
3. Send the SMS


Parameters to choose the best vendor:
1. Cost
2. latency
3. Uptime


Problem statement: SMS Service needs to guarantee the delivery of an sms
while choosing the best vendor at all times.